description: Smoking hot brunette lives out her fantasy of being snatched when she least expects it and gangbanged by five strong men in the middle of nowhere. After ordering her dream gangbang through a fantasy fulfillment service the company gets to work tracking her routine and researching the perfect time to grab her unaware. When her car breaks down "unexpectedly" in the desert she wanders to the only gas station for miles where she is taken down by the mechanic and taken to meet the other men. Tied and gagged in the back of a golf cart she is brutally fucked, slapped, shocked, and choked. Amazing breath play and a spectacular rough gangbang is exactly what Veronica ordered, and at Princess Donna's Fantasy Fulfillment Service, we always make sure you get what you pay for!
title: Stranded and Stuffed - Starring Veruca James
